column5: So, it's safe to say things that you want to say. Let's start with...ahhhhhhh YOU decide..going in now.
I'll be in as soon as I feed my face with some black eyed peas on white rice!  so if yer gonna say bad stuff aboot me, say it now!!!
Heck we like to say it to your face,  lol.
Roy, I can't believe we both posted this at the same time!!  Nice talkin to ya!!
I find it hard to believe anybody would bad mouth our good-natured, fun-lovin Dawg !!!
